LATEST JENNIFER ANISTON NEWS, PICTURES AND VIDEO UPDATES

Jennifer Aniston reveals her beauty secrets: The star, 53, begins her day with lemon water, does 'climbing cardio classes' and meditates This week the 53-year-old Morning Show actress shared with First For Women magazine exactly how she is able to look so youthful even when she works full time on her acting career. Jennifer Aniston reveals her beauty secrets

The Morning Show star Julianna Margulies, 55, looks youthful in her denim jeans as she adds a chic burnt-orange leather jacket when in NYC Julianna Margulies oozed chic when she was spotted stepping out for a stroll in chilly New York City early this week. The 55-year-old actress is best known for her lead role on The Good Wife. Julianna Margulies youthful in her jeans in NYC

Jennifer Aniston looks chic in black coat as she takes a break from filming Murder Mystery 2 in Paris Jennifer Aniston appeared chic on the set of her Murder Mystery 2 project in Paris, France. Jennifer Aniston channels Audrey Hepburn while filming in Paris

Jennifer Aniston looks chic in black coat as she takes a break from filming Murder Mystery 2 in Paris She started filming Murder Mystery 2 last month in Hawaii with her co-star Adam Sandler. And on Friday, Jennifer Aniston was seen on the set of the project in Paris, France . Jennifer Aniston takes a break from filming Murder Mystery 2 in Paris

Jennifer Aniston shows off her toned arms on Murder Mystery 2 set in Hawaii Jennifer Aniston glowed on set while filming Murder Mystery 2 in Waikiki, Hawaii last week. Jennifer Aniston shows off her toned arms in Hawaii

Jennifer Aniston sparkles in VERY flashy gold trousers as she thanks fans for birthday wishes after turning 53: 'Blessed girl over here' The actress, who turned 53 on Friday, rocked a pair of metallic fringe bell bottoms in a boomerang she posted to her account. Jennifer Aniston sparkles in VERY flashy gold bell bottoms

Chinese streaming platforms censor LGBTQ plot line about Ross's lesbian ex-wife and other sexually suggestive lines in 'Friends' sparking protests from fans on social media Major Chinese streaming platforms have censored an plot line in the popular TV series 'Friends,' which is hugely poplar in China, sparking protests from fans of the show on social media. Chinese streaming platforms censored LGBTQ Friends plot line

Justin Theroux posts video of Jennifer Aniston smoking while wearing 'cool blonde' T-shirt on her 53rd birthday... but swiftly deletes it He was married to Jennifer Aniston for two years but have remained friends since the end of their marriage. And on Friday, Justin Theroux wished his ex-wife a happy 53rd birthday. Justin Theroux wishes ex-wife Jennifer Aniston a happy 53rd birthday

Jennifer Aniston is 53! Reese Witherspoon shares a touching tribute for her Morning Show co-star: 'Her love of life, her humor are such a gift' 'When I think of Jen and all the wonderful adventures we have had together, I just smile. Knowing that @JenniferAniston is in the world makes me happy!' shared the Oscar winning actress. Jennifer Aniston is 53! Reese Witherspoon shares a touching tribute

Jennifer Aniston goes casual in all black as she boards a plane out of Hawaii after filming her comedy Murder Mystery with Adam Sandler The 52-year-old Friends star jetted out of Hawaii after finishing her scenes for Netflix's Adam Sandler comedy Murder Mystery. Jennifer Aniston jets out of Hawaii after filming Murder Mystery

Jennifer Aniston's adorable dogs Clyde and Lord Chesterfield won't stop 'smothering' her while she tries to workout at home The 52-year-old Morning Show star got more help than she bargained for when two of her dogs joined her for her morning workout. Jennifer Aniston's dogs won't stop 'smothering' her during workout

'Back to work with my buddy!': Jennifer Aniston and Adam Sandler look like a real couple as they share a photo on the Hawaii set of Murder Mystery 2 Jennifer Aniston appeared on Instagram on Monday to share a new post with her Murder Mystery 2 costar Adam Sandler as she wrote, 'Back to work with my buddy.' Jennifer Aniston and Adam Sandler work on upcoming Murder Mystery 2

Jennifer Aniston shows off her toned arms on Murder Mystery 2 set Jennifer Aniston glowed on set while filming Murder Mystery 2 in Waikiki, Hawaii on Tuesday. Jennifer Aniston, 53, shows off her toned arms on movie set

Jennifer Aniston proves she still looks youthful as she shows off her toned arms on Murder Mystery 2 set in Hawaii... a week before her 53rd birthday The Emmy winning actress - who will turn 53-years-old in just over a week - showed off her sensationally toned arms and slim figure in a fitting grey tank top and blue jeans. Jennifer Aniston shows off toned arms on set of Murder Mystery 2

Jodie Turner-Smith will be joining Jennifer Aniston and Adam Sandler for Murder Mystery 2... as Mark Strong and Kuhoo Verma also land roles On Tuesday it was announced that Jodie Turner-Smith and a slew of more talented actors have been hired to join the cast of Murder Mystery 2, which is filming in Hawaii. Jodie Turner-Smith will join Jennifer Aniston for Murder Mystery 2

EXCLUSIVE: Jennifer Aniston looks tanned and toned as she and co-star Adam Sandler spotted for the first time on set of Murder Mystery 2 in Hawaii On Monday, Jennifer Aniston and Adam Sandler were spotted for the first time while on the set of the sequel for the movie in Oahu, Hawaii. EXCLUSIVE: Jennifer Aniston and Adam Sandler spotted filming in Hawaii

EXCLUSIVE: Jennifer Aniston looks tanned and toned as she and co-star Adam Sandler spotted for the first time on set of Murder Mystery 2 in Hawaii They starred in the film Murder Mystery, which was released on Netflix in July 2019. And on Monday, Jennifer Aniston and Adam Sandler were spotted for the first time while on the set of the sequel. Jennifer Aniston and Adam Sandler spotted on Murder Mystery 2 set

Jennifer Aniston, 52, showcases evergreen looks as she shares make-up free selfie while wrapped up in towel The 52-year-old A-lister took to Instagram on Thursday morning to share a duo of selfies showing off her evergreen looks while going make-up free. Jennifer Aniston, 52, in make-up free selfie while wrapped up in towel

Reese Witherspoon and Jennifer Aniston react to their rival SAG Award nominations for The Morning Show The New Orleans-born 45-year-old and the 52-year-old Valley Girl will compete against each other for the female actor in a drama series trophy Reese Witherspoon and Jennifer Aniston react to rival SAG Award nods

The Morning Show continues! Jennifer Aniston and Reese Witherspoon's series gets renewed for a third season with a new showrunner attached Apple TV+ has renewed The Morning Show starring Jennifer Aniston and Reese Witherspoon for a third season. The series has additionally tapped a new showrunner for new season Jennifer Aniston-led The Morning Show renewed for a third season

Jennifer Aniston proves she's still VERY flexible at 52 while kicking up her heels in star-studded year in review montage Jennifer Aniston, 52, gave her 39.1M followers a lot to talk about as she shared an action-packed year in review montage of 'the little in between moments' ahead of New Year's Eve Jennifer Aniston showcases her flexibility during year in review post

Happy New Year's Eve, Hollywood style: Stars reveal what they are up to as 2021 comes to a close... with BIG hopes for a healthier 2022 The last day of 2021 fell on Friday with New Year's Eve celebrations kicking off early in the day as celebrities took to social media to wish their followers well in 2022. Happy New Year, Hollywood style: Stars reveal what they are up to

Jennifer Aniston unveils Clydeo, an adorable animated dog companion inspired by her beloved real-life pooch Clyde Jennifer Aniston, 52, unveiled an animated dog named Clydeo who is inspired by her real-life pooch Clyde and has his own Instagram account. Jennifer Aniston unveils Clydeo, an animated dog companion

Jennifer Aniston, Chris Pine and Jimmy Kimmel celebrate Jason Bateman's wife Amanda Anka's birthday at the Sunset Tower Hotel Jennifer Aniston was on hand to celebrate the 53rd birthday of her longtime pal and The Morning Show producer Amanda Anka. She embraced Amanda's husband Jason Bateman as she left the party. Jennifer Aniston and Jimmy Kimmel celebrate Amanda Anka's birthday

Alexandra Daddario, 35, flashes her large diamond engagement ring from Andrew Form, 52, when at The Hollywood Reporter event The brunette beauty wore a white outfit - a jacket and skirt - that made the most of her stunning finger as she let the bling talk for itself. Alexandra Daddario, 35, flashes diamond engagement ring

'I had to walk out at certain points': Jennifer Aniston recalls emotional reaction she had filming Friends: The Reunion The 52-year-old actress, speaking with The Hollywood Reporter , explained the nostalgia she felt reuniting with castmates for the reunion, which aired this past May on HBO Max. Jennifer Aniston had emotional reaction filming Friends: The Reunion

Jennifer Aniston receives the Sherry Lansing Leadership Award at The Hollywood Reporter's 2021 Women in Entertainment event She starred in ABC's Live in Front of a Studio Audience as Blair Warner on The Facts of Life. And one day later, Jennifer Aniston accepted the Sherry Lansing Leadership Award. Jennifer Aniston receives the Sherry Lansing Leadership Award

Jennifer Aniston gets VERY cozy with ex-husband Justin Theroux as they cuddle up together after enjoying a sweet reunion for Facts of Life Special After the show, it looked as though Jennifer, 52, and Justin, 48, spent time together and got cozy as they posed for a sweet picture together. Jennifer Aniston gets VERY cozy with ex-husband Justin Theroux

Jennifer Aniston gives a sweet nod to Friends during her appearance in Live in Front of a Studio Audience special: 'I'll be there for you' She led the all-star cast for ABC's Live in Front of a Studio Audience as Blair Warner on The Facts of Life. And during Jennifer Aniston's performance, the actress gave a nod to the show Friends, Jennifer Aniston gives a sweet nod to Friends during her appearance

Still good friends! Jennifer Aniston and Justin Theroux reunite for Facts Of Live table read... four years after they finalized their divorce Jennifer Aniston and her ex-husband Justin Theroux were in the same room for a table read of the Eighties sitcom Facts Of Life. They finalized their divorce four years ago. Jennifer Aniston and Justin Theroux reunite for Facts Of Live read

Jennifer Aniston leads casts of upcoming Live In Front Of A Studio Audience on Jimmy Kimmel Live as Kevin Hart jokes about walking because it's gonna be a 's***show' Less than a day before they perform two iconic episodes of television, the cast of Live In Front of a Studio Audience, lead by Jennifer Aniston, shared some laughs on Jimmy Kimmel Live. Jennifer Aniston leads casts on Jimmy Kimmel Live

'This stuff is magic!': Shoppers love Olaplex for transforming lacklustre locks - and Amazon has marked down the trial kit to just £21.76 Is Olaplex worth they hype? The Olaplex Hair Repair Trial Kit is now 25 per cent off on Amazon and contains four of the bestselling Olaplex products for just £21.76. The Olaplex hair repair trial kit is currently 25% off

Jennifer Aniston to lead star-studded live re-enactment of The Facts Of Life for ABC alongside Gabrielle Union and Kathryn Hahn The 52-year-old actress is leading the star-studded cast of live re-enactment of the beloved 1980s sitcom as she will be taking on the role of Blair Warner who was portrayed by Lisa Whelchel. Jennifer Aniston leads live re-enactment of The Facts Of Life

Jennifer Aniston plays hairdresser as she rubs leave-in conditioner into the locks of her longtime makeup artist Angela to plug her Lola Vie line The Morning Show star was rubbing product into the hair of her makeup artist Angela Levin as Aniston's stylist Chris McMillan looked on. She seemed to enjoy being behind the chair. Jennifer Aniston plays hairdresser

Chelsea Handler, 46, flashes her chest and toned tummy in a bikini as beau Jo Koy calls her 'the woman of my dreams' during vacation in Hawaii The close pal of Jennifer Aniston and Courteney Cox was enjoying a day at the beach in Hawaii with her boyfriend Jo Koy, who is also a comic. He said that she was the woman of his dreams. Chelsea Handler, 46, flashes her amble chest in a bikini

Jennifer Aniston shares some throwback snaps from the set of The Morning Show ahead of the Season 2 finale on Apple TV Plus With the Season 2 finale of Apple TV Plus' The Morning Show just hours away, Jennifer Aniston shared some throwback snaps from the set. Jennifer Aniston shares some throwback snaps from The Morning Show

Reese Witherspoon shares behind-the-scenes photos with Morning Show co-stars Jennifer Aniston and Julianna Margulies: 'The visionaries who brought this season to life' Reese Witherspoon, 45, posted a series of Instagram photos from The Morning Show set, including one with her gal pal Jennifer Aniston, 52. Reese Witherspoon and Jennifer Aniston on The Morning Show set

Jennifer Aniston is NOT 'the actress' in Taylor Swift's extended All Too Well, according to Jennifer Meyer Taylor Swift fans are still trying to find out who is the 'actress' mentioned in her extended version of All Too Well. Jennifer Aniston is NOT 'the actress' in Taylor Swift's All Too Well

Taylor Swift's fans think Jennifer Aniston is the 'actress' mentioned in new 10-minute version of her 'Jake Gyllenhaal break-up track' All Too Well Taylor Swift's devoted fans speculated that Jennifer Aniston is the 'actress' mentioned in the 10-minute version of All Too Well because they had a meeting around when she wrote the song. Taylor Swift's fans think Jennifer Aniston is referenced in Red song

Jennifer Aniston congratulates her Object Of My Affection co-star Paul Rudd on being named Sexiest Man Alive: 'We've ALWAYS known this!' Jennifer Aniston has congratulated Paul Rudd on being named People magazine's Sexiest Man Alive. The 52-year-old actor was awarded the coveted crown earlier this week. Jennifer Aniston 'happy' ageless Paul Rudd is Sexiest Man Alive

Jennifer Meyer puts her arm around ex-husband Tobey Maguire at splashy West Hollywood party... one year after she filed for divorce Jennifer Meyer was the belle of the night on Tuesday as her closest friends came out to honor her new collection with Moose Knuckles. One guest in particular stood out, however. Jennifer Meyer puts her arm around ex-husband Tobey Maguire

Jennifer Aniston flashes her bra as she models a sheer blouse while posing with Friends co-star Courteney Cox at party for designer Jennifer Meyer It appeared to be a mini Friends reunion on Tuesday evening at the famed Sunset Tower hotel on Sunset Boulevard in West Hollywood as Jen and Court partied. Jennifer Aniston flashes bra, poses with Friends vet Courteney Cox

Jennifer Aniston will be given the prestigious Sherry Lansing Leadership Award for her 30 YEARS in show business and philanthropy work Jennifer Aniston will receive the prestigious Sherry Lansing Leadership Award. The award will be handed to the Friends veteran at The Hollywood Reporter's annual Women in Entertainment breakfast. Jennifer Aniston will be given Sherry Lansing Leadership Award

Jennifer Aniston suffers a hilarious influencer fail while promoting collagen powder in new Instagram video - with one VERY glaring error Like many celebrities with a massive platform, the Friends actress, 52, uses social media as a way to sell a variety of products to her fans Jennifer Aniston's influencer fail while advertising collagen powder

Jennifer Aniston goofs around in the control room as she takes a break from filming on the set of The Morning Show in silly throwback video In video posted to her Instagram account, Jennifer sat in the control room and jokingly asked in the microphone, 'God are you there? It's me Jen.' Jennifer Aniston goofs around on The Morning Show set

Jennifer Aniston beams with delight as she enlists the help of her adorable pet pooches to reveal new LolaVie Leave-In hair care product Jennifer sported a classic white tee and jeans as she unboxed her brand from her living room while Clyde, her Schnauzer mix, appeared to be nursing a wound with a plastic cone around his neck. Jennifer Aniston enlists the help of pet pooches to reveal new LolaVie

Courteney Cox models the same clear aviator glasses her Friend Jennifer Aniston is known to wear as she heads to dinner in Santa Monica Courtney Cox cut a fashionable figure when she stepped out to dinner in Santa Monica this Tuesday evening. The 57-year-old Friends icon wore a black top decorated with a polka dot pattern. Courteney Cox models clear aviator glasses

Jake Gyllenhaal admits it was 'torture' filming sex scenes with real life crush Jennifer Aniston and reveals she would put a pillow between them as a barrier The 40-year-old actor revealed that he had such a crush on Jennifer Aniston, 52, that it was 'torture' doing love scenes with the actress in the 2002 film The Good Girl. Jake Gyllenhaal says love scenes with Jennifer Aniston were 'torture'

Jennifer Aniston turned down Kate Beckinsale's role in Serendipity to get out of rom-com mold... and worked with Mark Wahlberg in Rock Star instead The Morning Show actress turned down the role Kate Beckinsale eventually picked up in the 2001 John Cusack romantic comedy Serendipity because she did not want to be labeled a romantic comedy queen. Jennifer Aniston turned down the romantic comedy Serendipity

Jennifer Aniston fan girls over Foo Fighters visiting The Morning Show as she embraces frontman Dave Grohl: 'Mind officially BLOWN' The Hollywood superstar, 52, could hardly contain her delight in a slew of snaps capturing the rock superstars performing on her Apple+ show. Jennifer Aniston fan girls over Foo Fighters at The Morning Show

Jennifer Aniston was so hard on her Morning Show co-star Hasan Minhaj during an 'intense' scene he worried 'Rachel from Friends did not like me' Hasan admitted the scenes were so 'intense' between himself and Jennifer's character, Alex Levy, on The Morning Show that he couldn't gauge if she disliked him as a person or not. Jennifer Aniston intense on Morning Show

Jennifer Aniston reveals she's 'ready' to find love again after 'taking the time' to focus on herself following her split from second husband Justin Theroux in 2018 The 52-year-old actress said she's not currently dating, but has become more open to the idea of new love in her life as she chatted on Bruce Bozzi's SiriusXM show Lunch with Bruce. Jennifer Aniston is 'ready' to find love again after Justin Theroux

Round 2! Jennifer Aniston and Adam Sandler confirm they will appear in sequel to their 2019 Netflix feature Murder Mystery Development on a follow-up to the comedy film was initially reported just months after its initial release, although the involvement of the performers was not confirmed at the time. Jennifer Aniston and Adam Sandler will appear in Murder Mystery 2

Trendy fasting diets practiced by the likes of Jennifer Aniston and Benedict Cumberbatch may cut risk of heart disease and should be encouraged because they are 'simpler' than cutting calories, doctors say Professor Satchidananda Panda, from the Salk Institute for Biological Studies in California said people trying to lose weight should pay more attention to when they eat as well as what they eat. Simpler intermittent fasting better than counting calories doctors say
